_sText:
This map has been updated greatly. New sections have been added on so that it is now much less constrictive. The is able to be decompiled if anyone wishes to use this map for other types of game play. The map has also been greatly optimized to look much better. If you do not like the color correction in the map, just type "mat_colorcorrection 0" in console.


Note - any errors that occur as a result of decompiling is yours alone to sort out.
